{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "0c510036-9f70-4f3e-9d3a-081bbc46c526", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/0c510036-9f70-4f3e-9d3a-081bbc46c526@1.pkg/1772597678049/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597678947", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/0c510036-9f70-4f3e-9d3a-081bbc46c526@1.pkg/1772597678049/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597678947"}, "identifier": "0c510036-9f70-4f3e-9d3a-081bbc46c526", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>本题考查对法律的认识和理解。</p>\n\n<p>A:题干强调法律制定后必须有效实施，否则法律无法发挥作用，依法治国也难以实现，该表述直接对应“法律的生命力在于实施””，故A说法正确。</p>\n\n<p>B:科学立法是基础，但题干重点强调实施而非立法本身，故C说法不符合题意。</p>\n\n<p>C:题干未强调“制定法律轻而易举”，且法律的制定并不简单，说法错误</p>\n\n<p>D：“只能靠国家努力”过于绝对，法律实施需要全社会共同参与，故D说法错误。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（改编）“天下之事，不难于立法，而难于法之必行”。如果有了法律而不实施，或者实施不力，那么制定再多法律也是一纸空文，依法治国就会成为一句空话。这告诉我们（ &nbsp;）</p>\n", "title": "（改编）“天下之事，不难于立法，而难于法之必行”。如果有了法律而不实施，或者实施不力，那么制定再多法律也是一纸空文，依法治国就会成为一句空话。这告诉我们（  ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/0c510036-9f70-4f3e-9d3a-081bbc46c526@1.pkg/item.json?v=1755142718834", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple"